<h3>NFC Verification</h3>

<pre>
NFC Tag Format:

NDEF Record:
  Type: application/wia-credential
  Payload:
    - Version: 1
    - Credential ID: (8 bytes)
    - Verification URL: (truncated)
    - Quick verify hash: (16 bytes)

Scan Process:
1. Tap NFC tag
2. App reads NDEF record
3. Verifies quick hash locally
4. Optionally fetches full details
5. Displays verification status
</pre>

